rawContent:
Me: I feel #depressed.
Other person: Why, what happened?
Me: *Unable to explain but also deeply knowing it’s so much deeper and complex than one event.*

Asking why misses the point. Ask how to help. If they don’t know (which often happens), be an empathetic witness. #depression
